      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"generator\" content=\"pandoc\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes\" />\n  <title>Release Notes for GT911 Component Driver</title>\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\n      code{white-space: pre-wrap;}\n      span.smallcaps{font-variant: small-caps;}\n      span.underline{text-decoration: underline;}\n      div.column{display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;}\n  </style>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"_htmresc/mini-st_2020.css\" />\n  <!--[if lt IE 9]>\n    <script src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html5shiv/3.7.3/html5shiv-printshiv.min.js\"></script>\n  <![endif]-->\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"_htmresc/favicon.png\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-4\">\n<center>\n<h1 id=\"release-notes-for\">Release Notes for</h1>\n<h1 id=\"gt911-component-driver\"><mark>GT911 Component Driver </mark></h1>\n<p>Copyright \u00a9 2023 STMicroelectronics<br />\n</p>\n<a href=\"https://www.st.com\" class=\"logo\"><img src=\"_htmresc/st_logo_2020.png\" alt=\"ST logo\" /></a>\n</center>\n<h1 id=\"purpose\">Purpose</h1>\n<p>This driver provides a set of functions offered by GT911 TS component.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-8\">\n<h1 id=\"update-history\">Update History</h1>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section2\" checked aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V1.0.1 / 06-July-2023</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add reset of status register in multitouch function</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V1.0.0 / 31-May-2023</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-1\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>First official release of <strong>GT911</strong> Touch Screen component driver</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"sticky\">\nFor complete documentation on <mark>STM32 Microcontrollers</mark> , visit: <span style=\"font-color: blue;\"><a href=\"http://www.st.com/STM32\">www.st.com</a></span>\n</footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
